  "response": "```dockerfile
FROM rust:1.78 AS chef
WORKDIR /app
RUN cargo install cargo-chef
COPY . .
RUN cargo chef prepare --recipe-path recipe.json

FROM rust:1.78 AS rust-builder
WORKDIR /app
RUN cargo install cargo-chef
COPY --from=chef /app/recipe.json recipe.json
RUN cargo chef cook --release --recipe-path recipe.json
COPY . .
RUN cargo build --release

FROM python:3.11-slim-bookworm AS python-builder
WORKDIR /app
RUN python -m venv /opt/venv
ENV PATH="/opt/venv/bin:$PATH"
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir torch transformers tokenizers safetensors --extra-index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu

FROM debian:bookworm-slim AS runtime

LABEL maintainer="team@example.com"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.source="https://github.com/org/repo"
LABEL org.opencontainers.image.description="Rust + Python ML inference server"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    curl \
    python3 \
    libpython3.11 && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN addgroup --system --gid 1000 inference && \
    adduser --system --uid 1000 --ingroup inference inference

COPY --from=python-builder /opt/venv /opt/venv
COPY --from=rust-builder /app/target/release/inference-server /usr/local/bin/inference-server

ENV PATH="/opt/venv/bin:$PATH"

USER inference

EXPOSE 8080

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8080/health || exit 1

CMD ["/usr/local/bin/inference-server", "--port", "8080"]
